00:20:21,805 --> 00:20:26,643
Mr. Trask is our fearless leader,

255
00:20:26,684 --> 00:20:31,439
a man of learning,
a voracious reader.

256
00:20:31,523 --> 00:20:35,944
He could recite the "Iliad"
in ancient greek...

257
00:20:36,027 --> 00:20:40,323
