301
00:24:25,507 --> 00:24:28,510
Mr. Willis,
would you excuse us ?

302
00:24:31,721 --> 00:24:35,433
Have a nice Thanksgiving.

303
00:24:35,517 --> 00:24:37,477
Thank you.
You too, Mr. Willis.

304
00:24:37,560 --> 00:24:39,479
I will.

305
00:24:46,653 --> 00:24:48,947
Mr. Simms.

306
00:24:48,988 --> 00:24:52,742
