He loves to talk dirty.

416
00:31:26,569 --> 00:31:29,489
All right,
let's get to work.

417
00:31:38,456 --> 00:31:41,084
L-buckles
givin' you trouble ?

418
00:31:42,460 --> 00:31:44,754
